document.title: 2014 Conference Abstracts: Annual Undergraduate Research Conference at the Interface of Biology and Mathematics

author.organization: National Institute for Mathematical and Biological Synthesis (NIMBioS)

document.abstract:
Conference schedule and abstract book for the Sixth Annual Undergraduate Research Conference at the Interface of Biology and Mathematics

Date: November 1-2, 2014
Plenary Speakers: Joseph Tien, Associate Professor of Mathematics at The Ohio State University; and Jeremy Smith, Governor's Chair at the University of Tennessee and Director of the University of Tennessee/Oak Ridge National Lab Center for Molecular Biophysics
